{"tid":1456671,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上去呀]再係咁對面就贏喇屌！！！","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:06:58.000Z","uid":148608,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9259491c33d78fbae3bbd7d34361aebc1999aa83","tid":1456671,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"首先，三毛分化撚鬼全部死全家<br />\n<br />\n而家林奠黑警最希望係乜？<br />\n唔係你哋散水<br />\n唔係你哋留守<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係我哋內閧呀</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n快啲回想起無咁多鬼嘅時代，我哋係點強調「不分化，不篤灰，不割席」<br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去對面真係食花生睇我哋潰不成軍輕鬆贏！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所有嘢留畀現場每一個人決定</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係每一個人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n<br />\n「不分化，不篤灰，不割席」"},{"pid":"c93b2f8fe86d55498a0e4f4b9c850a130402a3bd","tid":1456671,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:15.000Z","msg":"快啲諗返起當初嘅信念"},{"pid":"c0496a9c980bf8ffd2a34a7aea4dacd289315fec","tid":1456671,"uid":31094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"Be water"},{"pid":"a0451012b9e4ba18ae9bf2da84c2e194c5dc940c","tid":1456671,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"由而家開始唔再開風向post"},{"pid":"b8ace0daf855f6b8d82e7f7b9623682bec2716bc","tid":1456671,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:04.000Z","msg":"唔好再喺連登拗走定留"},{"pid":"d647f45a9f0932734d66384394997a7a8f0fcf87","tid":1456671,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:38:45.000Z","msg":"唔好將我哋咁耐以嚟強調不分化嘅心血付諸流水"},{"pid":"5d89fc4ad42ee6c56db1f89beb42be0283de4b41","tid":1456671,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"aff0c0d